    <Paragraph>XAML defines a second grammar, DottedXamlName, that is used for property elements.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>String values that are of type DottedXamlName must conform to the following grammar:
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>DottedXamlName ::= XamlName ‘.’ XamlName
    </Paragraph>

